Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan vetoes budget
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wpxz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Nov 1981
Emergency bill allows government workers to be paid after President Reagan vetoes budget. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less